<!-- в”Ђв”Ђ PAGE в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">рџ“Љ 2025/26 Season</div>
    <h1>League <span>Standings</span></h1>
    <p>Live data from all top European leagues</p>
  </div>

  <div class="status-wrap">
    <div class="status-badge loading" id="statusBadge">
      <div class="status-dot"></div>
      <span id="statusText">Loading...</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LEAGUE TABS -->
  <div class="league-tabs">
    <button class="league-btn active" data-league="PL">
      <img class="lb-logo" src="/api/crest?url=https://crests.football-data.org/PL.png" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline'">
      <span class="lb-flag" style="display:none">рџЏґу Ѓ§у Ѓўу ЃҐу Ѓ®у Ѓ§у Ѓї</span>
      Premier League
    </button>
    <button class="league-btn" data-league="PD">
      <img class="lb-logo" src="/api/crest?url=https://crests.football-data.org/PD.png" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline'">
      <span class="lb-flag" style="display:none">рџ‡Єрџ‡ё</span>
      La Liga
    </button>
    <button class="league-btn" data-league="BL1">
      <img class="lb-logo" src="/api/crest?url=https://crests.football-data.org/BL1.png" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline'">
      <span class="lb-flag" style="display:none">рџ‡©рџ‡Є</span>
      Bundesliga
    </button>
    <button class="league-btn" data-league="SA">
      <img class="lb-logo" src="/api/crest?url=https://crests.football-data.org/SA.png" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline'">
      <span class="lb-flag" style="display:none">рџ‡®рџ‡№</span>
      Serie A
    </button>
    <button class="league-btn" data-league="FL1">
      <img class="lb-logo" src="/api/crest?url=https://crests.football-data.org/FL1.png" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline'">
      <span class="lb-flag" style="display:none">рџ‡«рџ‡·</span>
      Ligue 1
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- TABLE -->
  <div class="table-card">
    <div class="table-header">
      <img id="titleLogo" src="" alt="" style="display:none">
      <h2 id="titleText">Premier League</h2>
    </div>
    <div id="standingsBody"></div>
  </div>

</div>

<footer><p>&copy; 2026 Football Hub. All rights reserved.</p></footer>
<script src="/javascripts/chatbot.js"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/polish.js"></script>

<script>
  const leagueMeta = {
    PL:  { name:'Premier League', emblem:'https://crests.football-data.org/PL.png',  cl:4, el:5, ecl:6, rel:18 },
    PD:  { name:'La Liga',        emblem:'https://crests.football-data.org/PD.png',  cl:4, el:5, ecl:6, rel:18 },
    BL1: { name:'Bundesliga',     emblem:'https://crests.football-data.org/BL1.png', cl:4, el:5, ecl:6, rel:16 },
    SA:  { name:'Serie A',        emblem:'https://crests.football-data.org/SA.png',  cl:4, el:5, ecl:6, rel:18 },
    FL1: { name:'Ligue 1',        emblem:'https://crests.football-data.org/FL1.png', cl:3, el:4, ecl:5, rel:16 },
  };

  let currentLeague = 'PL';

  function setStatus(type, text) {
    const badge = document.getElementById('statusBadge');
    badge.className = 'status-badge ' + type;
    document.getElementById('statusText').textContent = text;
  }

  function updateHeader(code) {
    const meta = leagueMeta[code];
    const logo = document.getElementById('titleLogo');
    document.getElementById('titleText').textContent = meta.name;
    logo.src = `/api/crest?url=${encodeURIComponent(meta.emblem)}`;
    logo.style.display = 'inline-block';
    logo.onerror = () => logo.style.display = 'none';
  }

  async function fetchStandings(code) {
    currentLeague = code;
    const meta = leagueMeta[code];
    const body = document.getElementById('standingsBody');
    updateHeader(code);
    setStatus('loading', 'Loading...');
    body.innerHTML = `<div class="loading-box"><div class="spinner"></div><p>Fetching ${meta.name} standingsвЂ¦</p></div>`;

    try {
      const res = await fetch(`/api/standings/${code}`);
      if (!res.ok) throw new Error(`HTTP ${res.status}`);
      const data = await res.json();
      if (data.competition?.emblem) {
        leagueMeta[code].emblem = data.competition.emblem;
        updateHeader(code);
      }
      const table = data?.standings?.find(s => s.type === 'TOTAL')?.table;
      if (!table?.length) throw new Error('No data');
      renderTable(table, meta);
      setStatus('live', 'рџџў Live Data');
    } catch(err) {
      setStatus('error', 'вљ  Error вЂ” ' + err.message);
      body.innerHTML = `
        <div class="error-box">
          <div class="ei">вљ пёЏ</div>
          <p>${err.message}</p>
          <button class="retry-btn" onclick="fetchStandings('${code}')">рџ”„ Retry</button>
        </div>`;
    }
  }

  function renderTable(entries, meta) {
    const body = document.getElementById('standingsBody');
    let rows = '';

    entries.forEach(e => {
      const pos = e.position;
      const name = e.team?.name || 'Unknown';
      const teamId = e.team?.id || '';
      const crest = e.team?.crest ? `/api/crest?url=${encodeURIComponent(e.team.crest)}` : '';
      const mp = e.playedGames ?? 0;
      const w = e.won ?? 0;
      const d = e.draw ?? 0;
      const l = e.lost ?? 0;
      const gf = e.goalsFor ?? 0;
      const ga = e.goalsAgainst ?? 0;
      const gd = e.goalDifference ?? 0;
      const pts = e.points ?? 0;
      const form = (e.form || '').split(',').filter(Boolean).slice(-5);

      // Zone
      let zone = '';
      if (pos <= meta.cl) zone = 'zone-cl';
      else if (pos <= meta.el) zone = 'zone-el';
      else if (pos <= meta.ecl) zone = 'zone-ecl';
      else if (pos >= meta.rel) zone = 'zone-rel';

      // GD
      const gdClass = gd > 0 ? 'gd-pos' : gd < 0 ? 'gd-neg' : 'gd-zero';
      const gdText = gd > 0 ? `+${gd}` : gd;

      // Crest
      const crestHtml = crest
        ? `<img src="${crest}" class="team-crest" alt="" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'">`
        : `<div style="width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(255,215,0,0.08);flex-shrink:0"></div>`;

      // Form dots
      const formHtml = form.map(r => `<div class="form-dot form-${r.toLowerCase()}"></div>`).join('');

      rows += `
        <tr class="${zone}" onclick="window.location='/team/${teamId}'" style="cursor:pointer">
          <td class="td-pos ${pos <= 4 ? 'top' : ''}">${pos}</td>
          <td class="td-team">
            <div class="team-inner">
              ${crestHtml}
              <span class="team-name"><a href="/team/${teamId}" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">${name}</a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
          <td>${mp}</td>
          <td><strong>${w}</strong></td>
          <td>${d}</td>
          <td>${l}</td>
          <td class="hide-mob">${gf}</td>
          <td class="hide-mob">${ga}</td>
          <td class="td-gd ${gdClass}">${gdText}</td>
          <td class="hide-mob"><div class="form-wrap">${formHtml}</div></td>
          <td class="td-pts">${pts}</td>
        </tr>`;
    });

    body.innerHTML = `
      <table class="standings-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th class="th-team">Team</th>
            <th>MP</th>
            <th>W</th>
            <th>D</th>
            <th>L</th>
            <th class="hide-mob">GF</th>
            <th class="hide-mob">GA</th>
            <th>GD</th>
            <th class="hide-mob">Form</th>
            <th>Pts</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>${rows}</tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="legend">
        <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#3b82f6"></div>Champions League</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#f97316"></div>Europa League</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#22c55e"></div>Conference League</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#ef4444"></div>Relegation</div>
      </div>`;
  }

  // Tab clicks
  document.querySelectorAll('.league-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.league-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      fetchStandings(btn.dataset.league);
    });
  });

  // More dropdown
  function toggleMore() { document.getElementById('nav-more').classList.toggle('open'); }
  document.addEventListener('click', e => {
    if (!e.target.closest('#nav-more')) document.getElementById('nav-more').classList.remove('open');
  });

  fetchStandings('PL');
</script>
</body>
</html>
